  <div class="container-width py-16">
    <p class="eyebrow">Security posture</p>
    <h2 class="section-title mt-3">Current mail security controls</h2>
    <div class="card mt-6">
      <p class="text-muted">
        Domain registration is managed on
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
          href="https://www.spaceship.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          SpaceShip
        </a>. DNS and mail-related security policy is managed on
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
          href="https://www.cloudflare.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Cloudflare DNS
        </a>. Mail routing and mailbox service currently run through
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
          href="https://forwardemail.net"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Forward Email
        </a>.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
        Per
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
          href="https://forwardemail.net/en/private-business-email"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Forward Email documentation
        </a>
        and their
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
          href="https://forwardemail.net/en/blog/docs/best-quantum-safe-encrypted-email-service"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          security notes
        </a>, their service model includes encrypted mailbox storage and a zero-access architecture.
        Leter relies on that provider for the current mailbox layer.
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-5 grid gap-3 text-sm text-muted md:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-surface px-4 py-3">
          <span class="text-text">SPF</span> authorization policy
          (<a class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-text" href="https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/rfc7208">RFC 7208</a>)
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-surface px-4 py-3">
          <span class="text-text">DKIM</span> message signing
          (<a class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-text" href="https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/rfc6376">RFC 6376</a>)
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-surface px-4 py-3">
          <span class="text-text">DMARC</span> policy and reporting (aggregate and forensic/failure reporting)
          (<a class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-text" href="https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/rfc7489">RFC 7489</a>)
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-surface px-4 py-3">
          <span class="text-text">MTA-STS</span> transport policy
